# GigLink Mobile

A mobile app built with React Native (Expo) and TypeScript.

## Getting Started

1. Clone the repo
2. Install dependencies: `npm install`
3. Run project: `npx expo start`

## Tech Stack

Expo · TypeScript · Redux Toolkit · RTK Query · NativeWind · Moti · React Navigation

## Folder Structure

src/
├─ components/
├─ screens/
├─ features/
├─ store/
├─ theme/
└─ utils/
